dialogue: *Autumn leaves flutter around, it's the first day of school*
*Bell rings*

name: Player
dialogue: Wow, it’s finally the first day of senior year. I can’t believe time has passed by so quickly.

name: Teacher
dialogue: Welcome everyone, to our first day of school.

name: Teacher
dialogue: So over the summer, I’m sure many of you forgot the basics to JavaScript and CSS.

name: Teacher
dialogue: Let’s have a quick review, and then I’ll assign you all a small project.
*BANG*
*door opens*
Sorry Teacher! Got caught up in the main office.

name: Teacher
dialogue: No problem. Take a seat wherever you want.
Thank you.

name: Teacher
dialogue: Anyways, everyone, please log into your accounts.
Hey. Did I miss anything?

name: Player
dialogue: Nope, we just started.
Ah good. I’m LI1 by the way.

name: Player
dialogue: I’m [name].

name: Player
dialogue: By the way, I’ve never seen you around. Are you new?

name: LI1
dialogue: Oh yeah. I transferred here for my last year.

name: LI1
dialogue: I didn’t really like my old school. Didn’t suit me.

name: Player
dialogue: I see. Well, welcome to our school.

name: LI1
dialogue: Thank you!

name: Teacher
dialogue: Okay, so now for a quick partner project….

name: Teacher
dialogue: Here are the pairings.

name: LI1
dialogue: Oh wow. Looks like we’re together.

name: Player
dialogue: Yeah. Want to start today?

name: LI1
dialogue: Sure. After school at Starbucks?

name: Player
dialogue: Okay. See you then.
*3pm*

name: LI1
dialogue: HEY [name}. Wanna sit here or the back?

name: Choice 1
dialogue: Here is fine.

name: Choice 2
dialogue: Let’s move to the back.
*Sits*

name: Player
dialogue: So I was thinking our project could be a video game.

name: LI1
dialogue: I’m down for anything!

name: Player
dialogue: Let’s get started then!
*two hours pass*

name: LI1
dialogue: Wow we’ve been working for a while.

name: LI1
dialogue: Think it’s time to call it a day?

name: Player
dialogue: Yeah. I should get going.

name: LI1
dialogue: Should we meet again tomorrow or through text?

name: Choice 1
dialogue: We can meet tomorrow.

name: Choice 2
dialogue: I prefer through text.
*Next day at the cafe*
